<plot>When Juliet tells her older sister Anne that she will leave the family business to become a professional photographer, their already difficult relationship reaches breaking point. But this is just the prelude to even more dramatic events. How will Juliet react, torn between her lifelong dream and her devotion to the family? Will Anne eventually understand and support her little sister? And how can they find a new equilibrium that will go beyond life and death?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?041594</url></doc>
